OL,3,CFormer RAF officer says Chinook
OL,4,Ccrashed on 'show flight'
OL,6,FA former RAF officer has claimed a
OL,7,Fmilitary helicopter which crashed
OL,8,Fduring a flight from Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fto Scotland was on a "show flight" to
OL,10,Fprove its airworthiness.
OL,12,FTwenty-nine people - four crew and 25
OL,13,Fhigh ranking members of the security
OL,14,Fforces - were killed when the Chinook
OL,15,Fhit a hillside over the Mull of
OL,16,FKintyre in 1994.
OL,18,FUTV can reveal that former squadron
OL,19,Fleader Robert Burke tried to have his
OL,20,Fconcerns about the disaster raised in
OL,21,FParliament nearly 30 years ago.
