OL,3,CFormer RAF officer says Chinook
OL,4,Ccrashed on 'show flight'
OL,6,FChinooks were the Army's workhorses
OL,7,Fduring the Troubles. The helicopter
OL,8,Fused for this flight was a Mark 2
OL,9,Fversion, but it emerged there had been
OL,10,Fserious safety concerns surrounding
OL,11,Fthe aircraft.
OL,13,FA former RAF officer believes it was
OL,14,Fchosen to prove to the Army that the
OL,15,FMark 2 was safe following an upgrade.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
