OL,3,CFormer RAF officer says Chinook
OL,4,Ccrashed on 'show flight'
OL,6,FRobert Burke, who had been a test
OL,7,Fpilot at the time, said: "There were
OL,8,Fobviously major faults with that
OL,9,Faircraft, however the Mark 2 was sent
OL,10,Fto Northern Ireland as a gesture by
OL,11,Fthe RAF to show that everything was
OL,12,Fsorted."
OL,14,FPatricia Conroy said: "If my dad had
OL,15,Fhave known, any of those individuals
OL,16,Fhad been told look, this helicopter
OL,17,Fhasn't got a good track record, none
OL,18,Fof them would have got on it."
