OL,3,CFormer RAF officer says Chinook
OL,4,Ccrashed on 'show flight'
OL,6,FRecently it emerged files relating to
OL,7,Fthe disaster have been sealed for 100
OL,8,Fyears. Robert Burke saw some documents
OL,9,Fbefore they were locked away.
OL,11,FNow UTV has discovered he made a
OL,12,Ffailed attempt to have his concerns
OL,13,Fraised in the House of Commons back in
OL,14,F1998.
OL,16,FPatricia Conroy said: "This revelation
OL,17,Ffrom Mr Burke is truly shocking, it's
OL,18,Fdevastating."
