OL,3,CFormer RAF officer says Chinook
OL,4,Ccrashed on 'show flight'
OL,6,FThe allegations have boosted calls for
OL,7,Fa public inquiry, but in a statement,
OL,8,Fthe Ministry of Defense said: "The
OL,9,Faccident has already been the subject
OL,10,Fof six inquiries and investigations
OL,11,F... it's unlikely that a public
OL,12,Finquiry would identify any new
OL,13,Fevidence or reach new conclusions."
OL,15,FThe statement also says: "Neither the
OL,16,FRAF or the MOD recognise the term
OL,17,F'show flight' and have no information
OL,18,Fto support such a theory."
