OL,3,CFormer RAF officer says Chinook
OL,4,Ccrashed on 'show flight'
OL,6,FPatricia Conroy said: "It's heart
OL,7,Fwrenching, you know, it's really
OL,8,Fdifficult to think that we've been
OL,9,Fkept in the dark, and even now, all
OL,10,Fthis information is coming to light
OL,11,Fand people can still say no."
OL,13,FThe crash happened in foggy
OL,14,Fconditions, but it's clarity
OL,15,Fsurrounding the full circumstances
OL,16,Fthat victims' families are demanding.
